{"tid":2062344,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"粵語文學？","createTime":"2020-06-13T05:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T19:24:29.000Z","uid":312363,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7d173c379879c0a433bc401e81ada3a6a3905d","tid":2062344,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"一群文青借助港獨熱潮，眾籌十八萬元辦《粵語文學》雜誌。粵語文學？粵語這個詞已經有問題。廣東人叫白話、廣府話、西關話，客家人稱之為本地話。粵語是北方人的講法。故此該叫做白話文學、本地話文學。<br />\n文學是西洋詞，民國詞，本土詞叫文章。<br />\n故此是白話文章、本地文章。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;語言學家陳雲評論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DuAH9qt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuAH9qt.jpg&h=3619e19e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"521ed241e3d6f82e49046786d268543d7779bc27","tid":2062344,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"香港咁危急  有錢都幫左612/政治事啦<br />\n<br />\n文青會唔會太離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f14dc5ce89a46e8047201bc90f600b18e8ed76a","tid":2062344,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"521ed241e3d6f82e49046786d268543d7779bc27","tid":2062344,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"香港咁危急  有錢都幫左612/政治事啦<br />\n<br />\n文青會唔會太離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"搵食姐 犯法呀"},{"pid":"7bb35815ac256888a42a7ed4f002bf0cb9f159e1","tid":2062344,"uid":265229,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"521ed241e3d6f82e49046786d268543d7779bc27","tid":2062344,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"香港咁危急  有錢都幫左612/政治事啦<br />\n<br />\n文青會唔會太離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"又唔會嘅 之前大家都話長命戰爭要有人去保留我地嘅文化 <br />\n啲錢都係倒落海攬炒多架啦 有人肯比 比支持下本地文化發展咯"},{"pid":"c57c02d6ca2f0fc7b4a80717f8f0fac8979528af","tid":2062344,"uid":202844,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"521ed241e3d6f82e49046786d268543d7779bc27","tid":2062344,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"香港咁危急  有錢都幫左612/政治事啦<br />\n<br />\n文青會唔會太離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"絕不離地<br />\n文學係文化既載體之一。本土唔係政治咁簡單，仲有文化、語言......長期而言，本土文化同文學需要更被重視，咁先更增加到香港人嘅文化認同感。<br />\n<br />\n政治事件固然要有錢幫助，但文化界同樣需要金錢幫助。籍住呢家更多人講本土嘅時候，推廣粵語文學係個好時機。<br />\n<br />\n文化、文學應當被尊重。"},{"pid":"a8c8b168c80f0055a081f0eddc5d247828b3a3fa","tid":2062344,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T19:20:21.000Z","msg":"政事係為咗咩? 終極目標其實除咗自身生活幸福之外，仲係為咗維護文化呢個根。冇咗文化嘅根，其實政事就顯得唔再重要。"},{"pid":"d032ca8b24d7b5a88964cdac01999487f6254d71","tid":2062344,"uid":330227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"521ed241e3d6f82e49046786d268543d7779bc27","tid":2062344,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"香港咁危急  有錢都幫左612/政治事啦<br />\n<br />\n文青會唔會太離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T19:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文化嘅長遠影響力巨大"}]}